title: 6 New Cookbooks (gnv64)
description:
This is a collection of 6 new Cookbooks all in ePUB format:

1. Periplus Mini Cookbooks: Authentic Malay Cooking by Meriam Ismail (Dec 10, 2013) 
  
2. Better Than Vegan: 101 Favorite Low-Fat, Plant-Based Recipes That Helped Me Lose Over 200 Pounds 
   by Del Sroufe, Glen Merzer and Lindsay S. Nixon (Dec 3, 2013) 
  
3. Fish: 54 Seafood Feasts by Cree LeFavour and Antonis Achilleos (Sep 17, 2013)
  
4. Greater Mekong: A Culinary Journey from China to Vietnam by Nguyen, Luke (Dec 15, 2012) 
  
5. Maximum Flavor: Recipes That Will Change the Way You Cook by Aki Kamozawa and Alexander H. Talbot (Oct 8, 2013) 
  
6. The Ultimate Low-Calorie Book: More than 400 Light and Healthy Recipes for Every Day (Better Homes & Gardens) by Better Homes and Gardens (Dec 6, 2011)
